text: In case you hadn't heard - Oregon Story Board Demo Day is Friday!

attachments.title: Oregon Story Board Accelerator Demo Day
attachments.text: Oregon Story Board is proud to present the first class of our accelerator program, featuring five companies from the digital storytelling industry in Oregon. Come meet Built Oregon, Mountain Machine Studios, A Fourth Act, Studio Kate, and Chroma at the Hollywood Theatre for exciting presentations from five creative entrepreneurial teams. Want to know more about what it means to be a digital storyteller? We&#39;ll talk about how Oregon Story Board is working to support companiesÂ by providing the resources companies and entrepreneurs need to thrive. After four months in our beautiful glass &#39;fishbowl&#39; space inside of OMSI, hard at work together, our companies are excited to share their stories with you.
